'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 August 2000 [latest update: #2570] on 7 September 2000 at 8:52:21 pm'!"Change Set:		RepairGraphPaper-diDate:			7 September 2000Author:			Dan IngallsRestores the ability to make a graph-paper-style background for playfields and the world.  It had been broken by accidental double-nesting of the infiniteForm introduced in update #2537BetterGridding."!!Morph methodsFor: 'e-toy support' stamp: 'di 9/7/2000 20:44'!makeGraphPaperGrid: smallGrid background: backColor line: lineColor	| gridForm |	gridForm _ self gridFormOrigin: 0@0 grid: smallGrid asPoint background: backColor line: lineColor.	self color: gridForm.	self world ifNotNil: [self world fullRepaintNeeded].	self changed: #newColor.  "propagate to view"! !PasteUpMorph removeSelector: #pseudoDraw:withGrid:on:!